print("   ‚Ä¢ CLONE ME: Creates stationary clone that drops in place")
print("   ‚Ä¢ COPY PLAYER: Copies player appearance (server-side visible)")
print("   ‚Ä¢ Movable and minimizable GUI")
print("   ‚Ä¢ Works in most Roblox games")
